    }, {
      "type": 2,
      "style": 1,
      "custom_id": "role:481544681520365577",
      "emoji": {
        "name": "👅"
      }
    }]
  }, {
    "type": 10,
    "content": "## Learning roles\n- 🧑‍🎓 <@&469239964119597056>\n  if you'd like to be notified about exercises or lessons!\n- <:omega:486886779941683211> <@&649313942002466826>\n  if you'd like to be notified about new words!\n- 🤗 <@&683443550410506273>\n  if you'd like to take part in some events we host from time to time!\n- 🗺️ <@&637359870009409576>\n  if you'd like to be notified about interesting stuff we find regarding Greek dialects!\n- 📑 <@&800464173385515058>\n  if you'd like to be notified about reading linguistics papers relating to Greek (dialects or standard) with <@189036489265381387>"
