    "type": 10,
    "content": "## Misc roles\n- ☎️ <@&650330610358943755>\n  if you're a <@&350483752490631181> and you would like to take part in some statistical questions we ask from time to time\n- 🎮 <@&357714047698993162>\n  if you'd like to be notified about game discounts or events in <#357713113321046016>\n- 🗣️ <@&886625423167979541>\n  if you'd like to be pinged to join voice chats. You may also ping others.\n- 📚 <@&928364890601685033>\n  if you'd like to join the Book Club. You will be pinged when meetings take place."
